OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, BBC Scotland presenter Nick Sheridan   
OL,6, has died after a short illness.        
OL,8,FHis death at the age of 32 was         
OL,9,Fannounced by the broadcaster in a post 
OL,10,Fon X on Thursday morning.              
OL,12,FHe had presented programmes including  
OL,13,FReporting Scotland, Drivetime, the Nine
OL,14,Fand Seven Days since joining BBC       
OL,15,FScotland in 2018.                      
OL,17,FHead of news Gary Smith said Nick had  
OL,18,Fbeen a "wonderful colleague to those of
OL,19,Fus who have worked with him since he   
OL,20,Fjoined BBC Scotland in 2018".          
